      <p>Mafia Island is home to some of the most beautiful and least-crowded beaches in Tanzania. Unlike Zanzibar's packed shorelines, Mafia's beaches offer powdery white sand, turquoise water, and a sense of solitude that is increasingly rare in tropical travel. This guide covers every beach worth visiting, from the easily accessible stretches near Kilindoni to the remote, untouched shores of the northern coast.</p>

